{"tid":1805088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集體回憶］2002年元旦日Happy New Year事件","createTime":"2019-12-31T11:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T15:45:08.000Z","uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c18aa4e91b005dfcd2e76b9397fef1201a39118b","tid":1805088,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25A8%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=b25825d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n新年快樂事件是香港2002年元旦發生的一件警民衝突事件，事發地點為九龍尖沙咀近香港文化中心一帶的跨年倒數活動，一名14歲青年練志偉與一名警員互相掌摑，其後該名青年投訴被一名警員毆打，而警方則回應指<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只是二人互相輕拍面部並向對方祝賀「Happy New Year」</span></span>（新年快樂）。經過警方內部調查後，投訴警方獨立監察委員會最後接納警方的調查報告，指未能證實青年曾被毆打，只能證實雙方曾經講過粗口，所以終止調查工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/192904_838a2c6084bc9abea1e9055a038bac67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F192904_838a2c6084bc9abea1e9055a038bac67.jpg&h=73391575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=325774471598386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D325774471598386&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=38ca76f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=325774471598386</a><br />\n<br />\n那些年行得好前的香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7614db8eff3db75dff98a63904f76840c6f89c","tid":1805088,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:04:27.000Z","